br>3/20　HARU COMIC CITY 22　閃華春大祭 2017<br></br><span style=\"color:#9b7cb6;\">スペース：東5な04a「恋文とプラネタリウム*」<\/span><br></br><br></br>「薬研藤四郎という刀」<br></br>文庫本/200p（予定）/1&#44;200円（予定）/CP無/薬研藤四郎中心/地雷過多<br></br><br></br>表紙は棚桂ちなさん（**[user/869843<\/a><\/strong>）に書き下ろしていただきました。<br></br><br></br><span style=\"color:#9b7cb6;\">支部掲載分の「忘却症」「方向音痴」ほか二点の書き下ろしを含む、計四作品収録。<br></br>異質な空間、異様な病気、異常な状況を通して薬研藤四郎という存在を探る。<br></br>薬研藤四郎とは何者なのか。何を持って薬研藤四郎と名付けるのか。<br></br>誰が見るものが薬研藤四郎か。それは果たして薬研藤四郎なのか。<br></br>非日常から探る薬研藤四郎という存在について。<br></br><\/span><br></br><br></br>・忘却症「**[novel/6766226<\/a><\/strong>」<br></br>・方向音痴「**[novel/7163715<\/a><\/strong>」<br></br><br></br>ほか運がよければ既刊の「吉光薬研の放課後」があります。","restrict":0,"user":{"id":6003049,"name":"千夜子","account":"milkteapot","profile_image_urls":{"medium":"https://i.pximg.net/user-profile/img/2016/04/17/12/41/32/10815900_5021e498abaf49aaf0787dc85ca74c84_170.png"},"is_followed":false},"tags":[{"name":"薬研藤四郎"},{"name":"刀剣乱舞"},{"name":"閃華春大祭2017"},{"name":"HARUCOMICCITY22"}],"tools":[],"create_date":"2017-02-20T20:27:42+09:00","page_count":18,"width":764,"height":1018,"sanity_level":2,"series":null,"meta_single_page":{},"meta_pages":[{"image_urls":{"square_medium":"https://i.pximg.net/c/360x360_70/img-master/img/2017/02/20/20/27/42/61555580_p0_square1200.jpg","medium":"https://i.pximg.net/c/540x540_70/img-master/img/2017/02/20/20/27/42/61555580_p0_master1200.jpg","large":"https://i.pximg.net/c/600x1200_90/img-master/img/2017/02/20/20/27/42/61555580_p0_master1200.jpg","original":"https://i.pximg.net/img-original/img/2017/02/20/20/27/42/61555580_p0.png"}},{"image_urls":{"square_medium":"https://i.pximg.net/c/360x360_70/img-master/img/2017/02/20/20/27/42/61555580_p1_square1200.jpg","medium":"https://i.pximg.net/c/540x540_70/img-master/img/2017/02/20/20/27/42/61555580_p1_master1200.jpg","large":"https://i.pximg.net/c/600x1200_90/img-master/img/2017/02/20/20/27/42/61555580_p1_master1200.jpg","original":"https://i.pximg.net/img-original/img/2017/02/20/20/27/42/61555580